// data-modelling-ffi — C ABI wrapper around data-modelling-sdk v2.3.0
// for Java 25 Panama FFM (Foreign Function & Memory API).
//
// Architecture (mirrors yawl-rust4pm):
//   Java 25 Panama FFM (DataModellingL2 — generated by ggen)
//     ↓ downcall via MethodHandle
//   libdata_modelling_ffi.so  ← this crate (cdylib)
//     ↓ delegates to
//   data-modelling-sdk = "2.3.0" (pure Rust, no WASM)
//
// Pattern:  WCP-NB-03 / WCP-NB-04 native-bridge
// Correctness: dm_sizeof_dm_result + dm_offsetof_* probes verified at JVM startup
// H-Guards:  no TODO/mock/stub/fake/empty/lie/silent

